nfty$. The obtained results in this work are exactly the same as\nthose of obtained by the transfer matrix method which considers periodic\nboundary condition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Jan 2018 15:13:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-16"}
