th increased strain, while it is opposite for TA/LA\nbranch. By analyzing cumulative $\\kappa_L$ with respect to phonon mean free\npath (MFP), tensile strain can modulate effectively size effects on $\\kappa_L$\nin AsP monolayer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Jan 2018 15:18:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
